剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2016/" target="_blank">2016</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.19</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>陆远，一个在美国打拼、成为米其林三星餐厅主厨的中国汉子，在大多数人眼里他是个“混世魔王”，活得恣意，放浪形骸；在爱人眼中他却绝对是位另类“好先生”，专一长情又善良美国那场恶梦般的车祸没能要了他的命，倒是让他越活越自在。此次回国，陆远原本有三个目的：把因车祸去世的哥们儿彭海的骨灰带回国，让他落叶归根；</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/10373/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/5647/" data-original="http://pic.youku778.com/upload/vod/2019-01-16/15476445131.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">47</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/5647/">恋爱先生</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%9D%B3%E4%B8%9C------------/" target="_blank">靳东</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%96%8F%E5%BD%B1------------/" target="_blank">江疏影</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E4%B9%83%E6%96%87------------/" target="_blank">李乃文</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%BE%9B%E8%8A%B7%E8%95%BE------------/" target="_blank">辛芷蕾</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%A7%9A%E6%99%93%E5%B3%B0--------/" target="_blank">姚晓峰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/13/" target="_blank">国产剧</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>高端牙科诊所的牙医程皓身兼双重身份，业余时间还是一名“恋爱先生”，专门在情感的道路上帮人出谋划策，但自己感情生活却一片空白程皓在客户的一场婚礼前，偶遇伶牙俐齿的罗玥。二人状况百出，彼此嫌弃。但这一切，却在罗玥无辜遭遇“情感骗子”已婚的宋宁宇后，悄然发生改变。宋宁宇的妻子顾遥在被丈夫出轨的消息打击后黯</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/5647/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/51876/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-12-23/201812231545533061.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/51876/">恶人报喜</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%90%B4%E9%95%87%E5%AE%87------------/" target="_blank">吴镇宇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%96%8F%E5%BD%B1------------/" target="_blank">江疏影</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%83%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9F%BA------------/" target="_blank">郑中基</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BD%99%E5%AE%89%E5%AE%89------------/" target="_blank">余安安</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%B0%B7%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%AD--------/" target="_blank">谷德昭</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/7/" target="_blank">喜剧片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2016/" target="_blank">2016</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>查理（吴镇宇 饰）是一个假装残疾的骗子，冯仁炳（郑中基 饰）是一个无所事事的村长， 自称恶人的两人对初来村中的美女余真（江疏影 饰）一见倾心余真因怀孕和前男友反目而出走来到此地，无依无靠之时遂心生妙计，邀查理和阿炳来到家中共度晚餐。酒醉后余真故意让两人误以为与她促成好事导致怀孕，两人上当，难辨谁为亲</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/51876/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/60089/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2018-09-20/201809201537457965.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20181206期</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/60089/">恕我直言</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%94%A1%E5%BA%B7%E6%B0%B8------------/" target="_blank">蔡康永</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%96%8F%E5%BD%B1------------/" target="_blank">江疏影</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/3/" target="_blank">综艺</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>恕我直言蔡康永,江疏影</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/60089/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/55212/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/154773482411.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/55212/">天上的菊美</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%98%BF%E6%97%BA%E4%BB%81%E9%9D%92------------/" target="_blank">阿旺仁青</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%96%8F%E5%BD%B1------------/" target="_blank">江疏影</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E7%91%BE------------/" target="_blank">陈瑾</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%8B%97%E6%9C%88--------/" target="_blank">苗月</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2014/" target="_blank">2014</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>影片讲述了藏族基层干部菊美多吉短暂，但感人的一生他出身于四川省藏区的基层干部，虽然官职不大，但需要他担心的问题却不少，像牧民家的牛丢了，为当地修桥补路等在他人看来的“小事”,在他心中却是头等大事。而也正是由于过分操劳，使他患上了高血压等疾病，而这也没有能够耽误他为当地百姓服务，直至菊美在一次深入牧区</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/55212/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/16776/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2017-07-02/201707021499003922.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">20170709期</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/16776/">花儿与少年 第三季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E4%BA%95%E6%9F%8F%E7%84%B6------------/" target="_blank">井柏然</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%8B%A5%E6%98%80------------/" target="_blank">张若昀</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E6%9F%8F%E9%9C%96------------/" target="_blank">陈柏霖</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%A8%E7%A5%90%E5%AE%81------------/" target="_blank">杨祐宁</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B1%9F%E7%96%8F%E5%BD%B1------------/" target="_blank">江疏影</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%90%B4%E6%A2%A6%E7%9F%A5--------/" target="_blank">吴梦知</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/3/" target="_blank">综艺</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2017/" target="_blank">2017</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>前《花儿与少年》总导演廖珂担任总导演的新节目《#综艺•花样青春# 》近日在湖南卫视2017招商会上亮相该节目重新定义明星旅行真人秀，打破传统旅行节目叙事模式，大胆启用“#星素结合# ”人物设定，让明星和普通人一样去旅行。三位男明星，两位普通女孩，“星素+男女”迅速升温 ，开启旅行故事中无限的情感幻想</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fe